==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incunabulum
<hw>In`cu*nab"u*lum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Incunabula</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L.
<ets>incunabula</ets> cradle, birthplace, origin. See 1st <er>In-</er>,
and <er>Cunabula</er>.]</ety> <def>A work of art or of human industry,
of an early epoch; especially, a book printed before <sc>a. d.</sc>
1500.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

